# Falkiya Afreen's Portfolio - Environment Configuration Example

# Copy this file to '.env' (for local development) or configure this variable 
# in your hosting provider's Dashboard (e.g., Vercel, Netlify, Cloudflare Pages).

# Cloud Firebase Firestore Project ID
# 1. Create a free Firebase project: https://console.firebase.google.com/
# 2. Enable Cloud Firestore in "Test Mode"
# 3. Paste your Firebase project ID here
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-firebase-project-id
